flowchart TD
    PowerOn[Power On / Boot] --> Setup[main.cpp setup]

    Setup --> Prefs[Load Preferences\nsettings, Wi-Fi, history boot sequence]
    Setup --> HwInit[Init GPIO, piezo PWM, OLED, buttons]
    Setup --> SensorsInit[Init internal and external AHT30 sensors]
    Setup --> Prime[Prime first sensor read\nand first OLED update]

    Prefs --> NetworkDecision{Stored STA\ncredentials connect?}
    Prime --> NetworkDecision

    NetworkDecision -->|Yes| StaMode[STA mode\nstart mDNS\nsnowleopard.local]
    NetworkDecision -->|No| ApMode[Provisioning AP mode\nSSID SnowLeopard\nDNS captive portal]

    StaMode --> Web[Async web server routes]
    ApMode --> Web

    Web --> RootRoute[/\nStatus page in STA\nProvisioning page in AP/]
    Web --> SettingsRoutes[/settings\n/api/settings\n/api/settings_login/]
    Web --> HistoryRoutes[/history\n/api/history/]
    Web --> ProvisionRoutes[/api/provision\n/api/reconfigure/]
    Web --> AlarmRoute[/api/alarm_test/]

    subgraph MainLoop[Cooperative main loop]
        DNS[Process captive DNS\nwhen provisioning] --> Buttons[Handle buttons\nsetpoint adjust or password reset gesture]
        Buttons --> SensorPipeline[Sensor pipeline every 2s\nretry init, read AHT30s, apply offsets]
        SensorPipeline --> Control[Relay control\nauto/manual, hysteresis, lockout]
        Control --> History[Record history\n10s live ring + 60m snapshot ring]
        History --> Persist[Persist snapshot blob\nabout every 5 minutes when dirty]
        Persist --> Alarm[Temperature alarm beeper\nthreshold check and test cycle]
        Alarm --> Display[OLED renderer\nmode-specific screen]
        Display --> NetworkWatch[Watch STA disconnect\nand fall back to AP]
    end

    StaMode --> MainLoop
    ApMode --> MainLoop

    SettingsRoutes --> Auth{Settings auth enabled?}
    Auth -->|Yes| Cookie[Cookie-based settings session]
    Auth -->|No| Apply[Apply settings directly]
    Cookie --> Apply[Validate POST\nparse, clamp, persist, refresh auth token]

    Apply --> Prefs
    ProvisionRoutes --> Reboot[Save Wi-Fi creds\nforce history persist\nESP.restart]
    Reboot --> PowerOn

    History --> HistoryRoutes
    SensorPipeline --> RootRoute
    Control --> RootRoute
    Alarm --> Display